data.description: Amazing sought after home in Folsom Ranch. Ravine the most Popular plan in the area, offering a 3063 sqft, 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, two-car garage, with a two-story layout. Open floor plan, great for entertaining, it has a downstairs bedroom a full bathroom and office with 3 of the 4 bedrooms upstairs. Enjoy the open kitchen area, the walk in pantry and energy efficient appliances, as you entertain your family and guest. Seller paved the backyard, so enjoy the sunsets and BBQ'S with your family and guest. Less than a minute from Mangini Ranch Elementary School and Minutes from Highway 50, shopping and all amenities.
